  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Limbo is a 2D linear level game with six levels, each with a boss with a variety of moves. Defeat them with dodge, attack and other features!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy this game and you will play as a kung fu panda who will attack different bosses in 6 levels by wielding a bamboo stick, you can use dodge to dodge the boss's attacks and sneak up on them after the boss's attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras/f69e0f0545a780807bff54b468c740cd.avif?t=1730521574\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras_big/f69e0f0545a780807bff54b468c740cd.avif?t=1730521574 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras/f51866039db6f5c3d7355a17c916a2fd.avif?t=1730521574\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras_big/f51866039db6f5c3d7355a17c916a2fd.avif?t=1730521574 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras/3d9ab919567419a4072ec146da882f75.avif?t=1730521574\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras_big/3d9ab919567419a4072ec146da882f75.avif?t=1730521574 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras/249387107072ee58382f12ed9ec6b2ff.avif?t=1730521574\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270520/extras_big/249387107072ee58382f12ed9ec6b2ff.avif?t=1730521574 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\"